## üìÇ Current Progress: The Basics

Right now, I am focusing on the fundamentals of the language. You can find the code for these topics in the `Basic` folder.

| File Name | Concept Covered | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **`Hello World.java`** | **Syntax & Setup** | The classic starting point to ensure the environment is ready. |
| **`Scanner.java`** | **User Input** | Learning how to take inputs from the user using the `Scanner` class. |
| **`greaterthan.java`** | **Conditionals** | Using `if-else` logic to compare numbers. |
| **`for-loop.java`** | **Control Flow** | Understanding loops to repeat tasks efficiently. |
| **`String-sum.java`** | **Operations** | Basic string concatenation and arithmetic operations. |

